OL,3,CPlayer-coach relationships are
OL,4,C'sackable offences', says Aston Villa
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FAston Villa boss Carla Ward said a
OL,8,Fmanager should be sacked for having a
OL,9,Frelationship with a player, calling it
OL,10,Fa "complete abuse of power".
OL,12,FHer comments come as Leicester City
OL,13,FWomen are investigating their manager,
OL,14,FWillie Kirk, over allegations he had a
OL,15,Frelationship with one of their players.
OL,17,FIt is understood that Kirk has been
OL,18,Fsuspended pending an investigation
OL,19,Finto the allegations.
