OL,3,CPlayer-coach relationships are
OL,4,C'sackable offences', says Aston Villa
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FWard said it is the responsibility of
OL,8,Fmanagers to protect players and said:
OL,9,F"To cross that line is unacceptable
OL,10,Fand it can't happen."
OL,12,FShe added: "It makes me very angry
OL,13,Fbecause we are here to set an
OL,14,Fenvironment and a comfortable place to
OL,15,Fwork that the players feel safe,
OL,16,Fbacked and looked after, so I just
OL,17,Fdon't understand anyone that crosses
OL,18,Fthat line.
OL,20,F"You can't do it. It is a complete
OL,21,Fabuse of power.
