OL,3,CPlayer-coach relationships are
OL,4,C'sackable offences', says Aston Villa
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,F"We are in a moment where there is a
OL,8,Fmicroscope on the women's game and
OL,9,Fpeople have taken advantage of certain
OL,10,Fpositions, and I don't like that and I
OL,11,Fdon't think it is right."
OL,13,FAsked if a player-coach relationship
OL,14,Fshould be a sackable offence, Ward
OL,15,Freplied: "Yes. 100%."
