OL,3,CPlayer-coach relationships are
OL,4,C'sackable offences', says Aston Villa
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FWard, 40, who represented the likes of
OL,8,FSheffield United, Lincoln and Bristol
OL,9,FRovers during her playing days, said
OL,10,Fthe possible grey area of a player-
OL,11,Fcoach relationship ` given it is not
OL,12,Fillegal, providing no minors are
OL,13,Finvolved ` should be addressed in
OL,14,Fcontracts.
OL,16,FShe added: "It is an unwritten rule,
OL,17,Fand I am sure teachers don't have it
OL,18,Fin their contracts. But given where we
OL,19,Fare at now, and people don't
OL,20,Funderstand it, maybe put it in black
OL,21,Fand white so it is clear."
