OL,3,CPlayer-coach relationships are
OL,4,C'sackable offences', says Aston Villa
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,F"Say, you have got a director of
OL,8,Ffootball, and they have done wrong, or
OL,9,Fare doing wrong, and you know that,
OL,10,Fand a head coach or manager does it,
OL,11,Fyou can't go to that person because
OL,12,Fthe first thing they will do is rip up
OL,13,Fyour contract. I saw this as a player
OL,14,Fa lot.
OL,16,F"You hear things all the time and it
OL,17,Finfuriates me. The only way to clean
OL,18,Fup the game is to highlight it and get
OL,19,Frid of it."
